  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold leading-relaxed text-center text-opacity-80 text-base-content">Empower human coordination and cooperation in small or large communities, movements and co-ops.</div>

  <div class="relative max-w-screen-lg pt-8 mx-auto mt-24 overflow-hidden pb-28">
    <div class="relative">
      <div class="items-center gap-2 lg:mx-auto lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 place-content-start lg:grid-flow-col-dense">
        <div class="max-w-xl px-4 mx-auto sm:px-6 lg:py-16 lg:max-w-none lg:mx-0 lg:px-0">
          <div>
            <div class="">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-wide text-neutral-content">
                <span class="underline decoration-wavy decoration-amber-400 underline-offset-2">Coordinate</span> activities and tasks
              </h2>
              <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-md text-neutral-content text-opacity-60">
                A kanban tool to coordinate, prioritise and assign tasks, check the progress of a project, spot any possible blockers and see the work done. <br />
                Boards can be created for users of the same instance as well as across different instances. 
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="px-4 mt-4 md:mt-16 lg:mt-0 md:px-8">
