      <img src="/img/vf.svg" class="object-contain w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-4xl">
        <span class="block">Built upon open standards.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-6 text-base-content text-opacity-90">
        Bonfire cooperation is built upon <a href="https://www.valueflo.ws/" arget="blank" class="link bold">ValueFlows</a>: a set of common vocabularies to describe flows of economic resources of all kinds within distributed economic ecosystems.
      </p>
      <a href="https://www.valueflo.ws/" target="blank" class="mt-6 btn btn-outline">
        Read more about ValueFlows
      </a>
    </div>
